
<% if @giftee %>
<h3>You are Secret Santa for:</h3>

<p>-------------------------</p>
<h2><%= link_to "#{@giftee.firstname} #{@giftee.lastname}!", user_path(user_id: @giftee.id) %> </h2>
<p> Level: <%= @giftee.level %></p>
<p> House: 
	<% if @giftee.dept %>
		<%= @giftee.dept.name %>
	<% end %>
</p>
<p>-------------------------</p>

<p> Don't tell your assigned giftee about your role, it's supposed to be a secret.

<p>For ideas about what to give your giftee, please check out his or her profile and wishlist.</p>

<p>Here are some things <%= @giftee.firstname %> has wished for: </p>

<ul>
	<% if @giftee.wished_fors %>
		<% @giftee.wished_fors.each do |item| %>
			<li><%= item.name %> - <%= item.price %></li>
		<% end %>	
	<% end %>	
</ul>

<% else %>
 
<h3>Secret Santas haven't been assigned yet!</h3>

<% end %>

